title: QTFairUse Last Available Update
description: I have had alot of people asking for the last updated QTFairUse before they recieved a C&D letter. Well, here it is. The latest .cfg is included in the package, however, this will only work up until iTunes 7.5.0.20, so do not update iTunes any further, which is what I am doing. Everthing from the archive that was downloadable from the site is included. Have fun! It&#039;s a great program!
